&lt;p&gt;You will take ownership of meaningful client relationships, playing a pivotal role in driving engagement, deepening investor conviction, and contributing directly to revenue generation and business growth. This is a highly visible, client-facing position where your ability to combine market expertise with commercial acumen will have a tangible impact.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As part of a fast-scaling fintech redefining access to private markets, you will be at the forefront of a structural shift in how investors allocate capital, leveraging Moonfare’s digital platform to provide streamlined access to top-tier private equity, venture capital, and other alternative investment opportunities. This role is ideal for someone who thrives in a high-performance, entrepreneurial environment and is motivated by ownership, pace, and impact.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You will:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build, manage, and grow relationships with high-net-worth individuals, ultra-high-net-worth investors, and family offices, delivering a best-in-class client experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Act as a trusted partner to clients by providing insights, education, and guidance on private markets investments and portfolio construction&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support and execute private equity fundraising initiatives, including investor outreach, follow-ups, and pipeline management&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Take a proactive role in investor portfolio management, including portfolio reviews and identifying optimization opportunities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify and act on opportunities to contribute to revenue growth, including upsell and cross-sell initiatives&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prepare high-quality client materials, including investment memos, reports, portfolio updates, and presentations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify opportunities to improve internal processes and drive operational efficiency&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate cross-functionally with Product, Marketing, and Account Management teams to enhance the investor experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
